cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC 

This paper primarily focuses on the management of network slicing in local 5G networks, which falls under the category of network infrastructure (cs.NI). It also discusses the orchestration and configuration of network slices, which can be related to information theory (cs.IT) and system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of network slicing for different verticals, which can be related to multimedia (cs.MM) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
